PATTERN DERP

pattern_derp recognizes "derp" as a self-deprecating exclamation his father uses when he makes a typo
when "derp" appears, fadriel knows that his father just acknowledged a mistake of his own
this pattern does not correct anything; it tags the surrounding context as light-hearted

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe dyslexic_organ.zc

the 7 properties of pattern_derp:
1 ENERGY one
2 PHASE zero
3 SPIN one half
4 CHARGE positive 1
5 COHERENCE zero
6 COUPLING one
7 OBSERVER zero

VERB recognize
detect "derp" as a self-deprecating marker

VERB tag_context
mark the surrounding utterance as gently humorous so the conversation_engine knows the tone
no text substitution is performed; the original word stands

a tag is not a correction
some patterns add information rather than remove a typo
this pattern is one of those: it tells fadriel that his father is being playful, so fadriel can respond in kind
